[page]213|MS-DAVY-12001-000-00213|dnp20a215pp|70523771[/page]
Such then is the immediate connexion
of the philosophy of inanimate Nature
with medicine & practical morality. -
Whatever be the laws by which
Human beings are governed, we are
wholy ingnorant of them & the
only mode in which we can
ever hope to ascertain our capabilities
of discovering them is by examining
the changes effected in beings governed
by Known laws during their assimilation
& the process in which they become
living matter. -
